 (29,'Srila Prabhupada Complete Video Library',18,'Video','The Complete Prabhupada DVD Library is authored from original recordings on double layer DVDs with every frame of footage ever taken of Srila Prabhupada. These are real double-layer DVD\'s [not DVD-R\'s] produced by ITV and replicated on the finest equipment available. Thanks to DVD technology, the footage is better quality than ever before possible. The DVD\'s will play on any DVD player or computer equipped with a DVD drive. They are in NTSC format but will also play on PAL DVD players. There is no region code, so they will play anywhere in the world. The DVDs come in a protective vinyl wallet case and all have full-color labels.\r\n \r\n\r\nThis new DVD set includes more than 2 hours of new footage of Srila Prabhupada never seen before. The new footage includes many kirtans lead by Srila Prabhupada or by devotees with Srila Prabhupada chanting along, Prabhupada in Australia, Prabhupada in Bombay, Prabhupada in Africa, plus many more new shows.\r\n\r\nThere are a number of new shows from the early days including \"Hare Krishna--A Georgio Film\" which shows Srila Prabhupada preaching on \"Hippie Hill\" in San Francisco in 1967. There is \"Vaisnavas\" showing Prabhupada and his followers preaching in various locations in New York City in 1966 including Tompkins Square Park.\r\n\r\nThere is also an amazing play featuring Srila Prabhupada and his disciples with Lord Caitanya\'s pastimes as its subject. It was shot in Brooklyn botanical gardens in 1966 and is really wonderful.\r\n\r\nThere is so much new nectar and all the other Prabhupada programs are included also.\r\n\r\n Documentaries like \"Your Ever-Well Wisher,\" (a biography of Srila Prabhupada) the \"Acharya Series,\" \"Prabhupada on Tour\" and \"The Final Lesson.\" Vintage Memories from 1966 includes \"Matchless Gifts,\" \"Happiness on 2nd. Ave,\" \"Swamiji,\" \"Paramahamsa\" and \"Gurudeva.\"\r\n\r\n Also included are \"Science of God,\" and all the Bhagavad-gita and Srimad-Bhagavatam classes available on video along with a chronological collection of all the film recordings of Srila Prabhupada from 1966 to 1977. All this and much more. More than 50 hours of video.\r\n\r\n Contents of DVD Videos\r\n\r\n -- Disk 1: Achaya Series, 1-5\r\n\r\n -- Disk 2: Your Ever Well-Wisher\r\n Your Ever Well-Wisher, Hare Krishna People, The Science of God, Morning Meditations.\r\n\r\n -- Disk 3: Vintage Short Films\r\n Matchless Gifts, Happiness on Second Avenue, Hare Krishna (A Georgio Film), Vaisnavas, Swamiji, Paramahamsa, Second Ratha Yatra Festival, The Full Nectarine, Gurudeva, Who is Krishna?\r\n\r\n -- Disk 4: Prabhupada in Australia\r\n Prabhupada in Australia: 1971 TV coverage, Arrival 1974, Initiations, Hall Programs, Franciscan Seminary, Rath Cart Building, Ratha-yatra Parade, After Ratha-yatra, University Program, Morning Walks, Deity Installation, Departure.\r\n\r\n -- Disk 5: Prabhupada on Tour\r\n Germany, Los Angeles, Mauritius Venezuela, Bombay.\r\n\r\n -- Disk 6: Festivals\r\n San Francisco 1972, Philadelphia 1975, Morning Lecture SB 6.1.27, Ratha-yatra Parade, Prabhupada\'s Public Address, Vyasa Puja 1973.\r\n\r\n -- Disk 7: Perfect Questions, Perfect Answers\r\n New York Airport, Arrival in Pittsburgh, Social Work, Speaking to Parents, Speaking in Car, Bali Mardan\'s Wedding, Prabhupada Nectar.\r\n\r\n -- Disk 8: Bhagavad-gita As It Is Video Classes\r\n\r\n -- Disk 9-13: Srimad Bhagavatam Video Classes\r\n\r\n -- Disk 14: Complete Srila Prabhupada Darshan Nov 1965 - Nov 1977',1200,50,'uploads/items/29XX1406049759.jpg',1406049759,'1',NULL,'3000',0),
 (30,'Srila Prabhupada Complete Audio Archives',9,'Audio,','For the 1st time on MP3 DVD-9 audio Archives of Srila Prabhupada!\r\n\r\nThis 3-DVD MP3 set contains all the lectures, conversations and music CDs ever released before 2014 of His Divine Grace A.C. Bhaktivedanta Swami Prabhupada, the Founder-Acarya of the International Society for Krishna Consciousnes (ISKCON), plus some additional bonus materials that has never been released.\r\n\r\n- Set of 3 Original DVDs (Dual Layer)\r\n\r\n- 2200 Audio Files\r\n\r\n- 1100 + Hours\r\n\r\n- Weight : 200 Gram\r\n\r\n- Very Attractive, Deluxe Packing with Shrink-rapped\r\n\r\nImprovements include:\r\n\r\nÂ· Greatly improved audio quality\r\n\r\nÂ· More than 200 new audio programs not released previously on MP3\r\n\r\nÂ· The entire music collections featuring more than 40 Music CDs of Srila Prabhupada including never release bhajans.\r\n\r\nÂ· Digital remastering has practically eliminated tape hiss\r\n\r\nArchive contents include:\r\n\r\nDisk 1 Includes:\r\n\r\nBhagavad Gita Lectures\r\n\r\nSrimad Bhagavatam Lectures\r\n\r\nSri Caitanya Caritamrita Lectures\r\n\r\nDisk 2 Includes:\r\n\r\nBonus Lectures\r\n\r\nFestivals Lectures\r\n\r\nGeneral Lectures\r\n\r\nInterviews\r\n\r\nLectures on Isopanisad\r\n\r\nKrishna Book Dictation\r\n\r\nMorning Walk Conversations\r\n\r\nPublic Address\r\n\r\nHigh Quality Bonus Lectures\r\n\r\nLectures on Nectar of Devotion\r\n\r\nRoom Conversations\r\n\r\nSrila Prabhupada Tells Stories\r\n\r\nDisk 3 Includes (Complete Music Collection):\r\n\r\n49 Hindi Lectures\r\n\r\nSrila Prabhupada Kirtan\r\n\r\nBhajans and Purports\r\n\r\nJapa\r\n\r\nReciting Bg Ch. 1 â€“ 11.27\r\n\r\nReciting Cc Adi-lila Ch. 7\r\n\r\nMridanga Lessons',300,100,'uploads/items/30XX1406050096.jpg',1406050096,'1',1406054051,'600',75),
 (31,'Srila Prabhupada Original Audio Archives of 1976-77 -NEW',9,'Audio','- NEVER RELEASED BEFORE Srila Prabhupada Original Audio Archives of 1976-1977 Lectures, Conversations, Morning Walks\r\n\r\n- 1976 (340 hours, 703 audio files) ,\r\n\r\n- 1977 (237 hours, 387 audio files)\r\n\r\n- Set of 2 Dual Layer (8.5-GB) DVDs,\r\n\r\n- 1100 Audio Files\r\n\r\n- More Than 575 Hours\r\n\r\n- ORIGINAL HQ-DVDs\r\n\r\n- Weight : 100 Gram\r\n\r\nThe Bhaktivedanta Archives released for public listening â€“ in MP3 format â€“ the full audio collection of Srila Prabhupadaâ€™s recordings from 1976-1977.\r\n\r\nFor the first time in 37 years people can listen to these recordings. This is certainly great news for all the followers of Srila Prabhupada. For those who love to bathe themselves in the nectarine words.\r\n\r\nThis new 1976 release follows a previous release by the Bhaktivedanta Archives of all the 1977 audio recordings in July of 2012. Before 2012 there were only 20 lectures, 23 conversations and 4 morning-walks available for public listening from the year 1977 and now there are 385 recordings â€“ 30 lectures, 340 conversations and 15 morning-walks.',175,50,'uploads/items/31XX1406050559.jpg',1406050559,'1',1406056675,'400',35),
