 (80,'Srila Prabhupada in Australia (Preaching Tour)',21,'','The \"Prabhupada in Australia\" DVD is completely new. It contains hours of never-released before footage and completely new shows including the installation of Mahaprabhu in Melbourne, Prabhupadas visit to the Franciscan Seminary, the eventful college preaching engagement at Latrobe University, peaceful morning walks, hall programs, and of course the Ratha Yatra Festival and the after party.\r\n \r\nContents of the DVD:    \r\n \r\nSrila Prabhupada in Australia: \r\n-1971 TV coverage \r\n- Arrival 1974, \r\n- Initiations\r\n- Hall Programs\r\n- Franciscan Seminary\r\n- Rath Cart Building\r\n- Ratha-yatra Parade\r\n- After Ratha-yatra\r\n- University Program\r\n- Morning Walks, Deity Installation, Departure. \r\n    \r\nDuration: Over 4 hrs',85,10,'uploads/items/80XX1406313329.jpg',1406313329,'1',NULL,'200',25),
 (81,'Laws of Nature',6,'','Karma and the laws governing nature are a baffling, entangling force that shackles us to this world. Understand the workings of the laws and the Lawmaker, get free of the restraints, and attain real freedom.\r\n\r\nThis absorbing book explores the age-old mysteries of karma and reincarnation, free will and destiny, enlightenment, and liberation.\r\n\r\nSoftbound, 97 pages, glossary, index, 5.5\" x 8\".',45,10,'uploads/items/81XX1406314161.jpg',1406314161,'1',NULL,'',20),
 (82,'Narada-Bhakti-Sutra: The Secrets of Transcendental Love',6,'','These ancient aphorisms about bhakti by the renowned Vedic sage Narada are finally available in English. Discover these unearthed treasured secrets.\r\n\r\nLove of God, bhakti, is sometimes called the \"storehouse of nectar,\" and there is nothing more magnificent or pleasing to the soul. Our spirit hankers to gain the freedom of the transcendental realm, but without the gift of instruction from realized souls on the other side, we will remain here.\r\n\r\nNarada extends a helping hand with these brief, transforming instructions.\r\n\r\nSoftbound, 213 pages, original Sanskrit text, 5.5\" x 8.5\".\r\nCompany: BBT\r\nISBN: 0-89213-273-6',75,10,'uploads/items/82XX1406314461.jpg',1406314461,'1',NULL,'',25);
